stories_text_raw:

As a developer, I want to update submission errors, so that they accurately represent FABS errors.

As a developer, I want to prevent DABS banner messages, so that they do not interfere with the user experience.
As a developer, I want to provide read-only access, so that users can view data without modifying it.

As a developer, I want to update status labels, so that they accurately reflect the status.
As a developer, I want to provide submission periods, so that users can plan accordingly.
As a developer, I want to create a landing page, so that users can navigate to either FABS or DABS pages.
